<!--<h4>Obverse.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svastiśrī permmāḍi prithuvīrājyaṁgeye
<lb n="2"/>pulināḍu mayimanapalla
<lb n="3" break="no"/>vareyarāḷe ma
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṅgalada tuṟugoḷoḷ beḷatūra<note n="2-1">The letters in the other.</note> 
</p>

<!--<h4>Reverse.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="5"/><hi rend="bold">rāca</hi> pari<unclear>yaṭṭaṁ</unclear> palarumanā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ntāḷu satta Ivaṅge Arasuṁ Ūru
<lb n="7" break="no"/>miṟdu kalnāḍaṁ Emkoḷa<unclear>ka</unclear>ḻa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>Idanaḻivō bāraṇāsi
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ya naḻida pañcamahāpāta
<lb n="10" break="no"/>kaṁ Idaṁ salisidō Asvamē
<lb n="11" break="no"/>dada phalaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> Idakke pi
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ri konda <unclear>pāpa</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
</p>

